      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between simulation and experiment was not formally assessed across the COU2 operating envelope. The single available experimental reference point (3 L/min / 3000 RPM) was matched in simulation setup, but the four remaining operating points lack experimental counterparts against which input equivalency could be verified. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Not assessed; required level 4 unmet."
